OmniGBDT is a fork of the original GBDT-MO project by Zhendong Zhang and
Cheolkon Jung.

This repository includes packaging, distribution, documentation, testing, and
maintenance changes for the OmniGBDT fork, while preserving substantial parts
of the original training and inference implementation from GBDT-MO.

The original upstream MIT license notice from Zhendong Zhang is preserved in
LICENSE.upstream.
